{"word":"H1626 - גֵּרָה - gêrâh - gay-raw' - Gerah - கேரா","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>גֵּרָה"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>gêrâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>gay-raw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Gerah / கேரா"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கேரா - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"gerah, a weight"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H1641 - גָּרַר - gârar - gaw-rar'/1641\">H1641</a> (as in <a href=\"#/H1625 - גֵּרָה - gêrâh - gay-raw'/1625\">H1625</a>); properly (like <a href=\"#/H1620 - גַּרְגַּר - gargar - gar-gar'/1620\">H1620</a>) a <i>kernel</i> (round as if <i>scraped</i>), that is, a <i>gerah</i> or small weight (and coin): - gerah."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1620 - גַּרְגַּר - gargar - gar-gar'/1620\">H1620</a>, <a href=\"#/H1621 - גַּרְגְּרֹות - gargᵉrôwth - gar-gher-owth'/1621\">H1621</a>, <a href=\"#/H1625 - גֵּרָה - gêrâh - gay-raw'/1625\">H1625</a>, <a href=\"#/H1626 - גֵּרָה - gêrâh - gay-raw'/1626\">H1626</a>, <a href=\"#/H1641 - גָּרַר - gârar - gaw-rar'/1641\">H1641</a>, <a href=\"#/H1642 - גְּרָר - Gᵉrâr - gher-awr'/1642\">H1642</a>, <a href=\"#/H4050 - מְגֵרָה - mᵉgêrâh - meg-ay-raw'/4050\">H4050</a>"}]}